MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2008-0147. State ex rel. Coughlin v. Summit Cty. Bd. of Elections.

In Mandamus and Prohibition. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus/prohibition involving an expedited election matter. Upon consideration of relators’ application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
